    lessons: ["Holiness that only shows up in church is not holiness — it is performance.", "The small decisions of daily life reveal the true condition of the heart.", "Holy living requires deliberate choices about what you feed your mind.", "A believer's language is one of the most visible indicators of spiritual maturity."],
    prayer: "Lord, make me holy in my home, my workplace, my entertainment choices, and my speech. Let the fruit of Your Spirit be visible in every area of my daily life.",
    conclusion: "Holiness is not an upgrade for advanced believers — it is the standard for every follower of Christ. Begin today by identifying one area of daily life that does not yet reflect the character of God, and surrender it to Him.",
