    excerpt: "A teaching on spiritual gifts — every believer has been given gifts by the Holy Spirit for the benefit of the church, and every gift must be discovered, developed, and deployed.",
    seoTitle: "Understanding Spiritual Gifts: Every Believer Has a Role",
    seoDescription: "Learn about spiritual gifts — how to discover yours, how to develop them, and why every gift matters for the health and mission of the church.",
